           </ol>
         </li>
         <li><em>0.9.4</em>
           <ol>
               <li>Able to show changelist details from the file history view.
               Right-click on the history entry and select <i>Describe Changelist</i>, or
               click the info icon on the history window toolbar.
               <li>Fixed issue with stored Perforce server configuration causing the project
               list to not load correctly.  This only affected projects that were opened
